Description: Here we have an amazing pair of Casanova SC6 glasses/ sunglasses in pretty much new condition! I bought them new with tags and only wore them 2 or 3 times. They really are fantastic This is an extremely rare pair of from the 1980s, simbolismo range by Casanova. They are inspired by the 18th century Venetian carnival. These glasses have become extremely desired by eyewear and art collectors worldwide. There were only 1000 of these made & this was 30 years ago!! If you wanted a pair before these were listed, you'd have to pay over 800 for them. This is a rare chance to grab a bargain piece of art that you can wear!! Lenses are non prescription clear, in very good condition. Can easily be changed to your prescription or indeed to sunglasses. Casanova hard case included. This is not a case for this model, but fits very well Bidding starting very low. Good luck & feel free to make me an offer higher than auction starting price if you would like them sooner!
